{"tid":1756633,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone 7入水後無顯示，換左3隻mon都唔得，點解會咁？ （免費幫各位手足整iphone）","createTime":"2019-11-26T06:23:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-12T09:18:49.000Z","uid":320119,"like":103,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"e3f313dbf4add116d01ef1a72fdeca28feaa01f9","tid":1756633,"uid":320119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T06:23:00.000Z","msg":"我p牌推唔到舊post，唔知我係邊個既巴絲可以睇番：<br />\n專門整iPhone壞主板之你問我答（義士免費整iPhone)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1559974\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1559974</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有位手足部iphone 7入水後無顯示<br />\n佢自己換左3隻mon都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以拎比我幫佢整<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EBH29rq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEBH29rq.png&h=5cc8e1c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n順便係到建議大家，如果本身唔係做呢行既<br />\n唔好自己換配件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為一來電池有一定危險，拆爛會爆炸燒傷自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n二來電子野好脆弱，好容易唔小心整壞其他野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以電話壞左最好直接拎比信得過既師傅整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xP4Uf7K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxP4Uf7K.png&h=04075d4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我再用另一個mon測試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見到係正常開機電流，說明主板已經開機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係個mon無顯示<br />\n證明主板既顯示電路有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PVFoTUZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPVFoTUZ.png&h=f6e9221c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n測下顯示座既阻值<br />\n阻值既數據會話到比我地知問題出係邊一路電路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KhbLnOK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKhbLnOK.png&h=d09b26f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n測到顯示座第一腳既阻值只有0.003（正常有0.6xx)<br />\n說明呢一路有短路既地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n已經搵到問題既方向了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1UOxNge.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1UOxNge.png&h=2c3373f0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5FvcNgi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5FvcNgi.png&h=6faa6caa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇番電路圖<br />\n第一腳係由mon供電ic將5.7v電送去顯示座<br />\n顯示座再送去我地既mon<br />\n呢一路短路所以無供電，難怪會無顯示<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mZB7Bbg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmZB7Bbg.png&h=cf2cb20e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n拆塊板出黎<br />\n見到5.7v供電電容既位置嚴重入水<br />\n初步懷疑電容短路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sk7e0Hw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsk7e0Hw.png&h=bd0911fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以上係顯微鏡既世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n電容短路會發熱，松香煙遇熱會溶<br />\n所以落松香煙再加電就可以搵到短路既電容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拆左短路既電容，再換番粒新電容<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8g0DHYq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8g0DHYq.png&h=82f2475c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n再測顯示座第一腳<br />\n今次阻值正常番了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jtsnqb6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJtsnqb6.png&h=b82a74fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n開機測試<br />\n有番顯示了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n整機既巴打絲打可以tg或ig聯絡我，<span style=\"color: red;\">一律免費</span><br />\nIg: iphonemotherboardhk <br />\nTg:<a href=\"https://t.me/IphoneMotherboardhk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FIphoneMotherboardhk&d=%2BSgL3cCD37R2%2BMUJ9ALV07eFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=5f0a8dc0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/IphoneMotherboardhk</a>"},{"pid":"28bc854432fdee14c0aa498dc828eee6cc36a74e","tid":1756633,"uid":46232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T06:25:18.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e421c399c781cf5b89dcf50b2426dec41b00025d","tid":1756633,"uid":30990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T06:25:44.000Z","msg":"推   <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />全靠巴打部機先無事"},{"pid":"22d8434cc20dc876432810f3079e736643d8bc32","tid":1756633,"uid":320119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e421c399c781cf5b89dcf50b2426dec41b00025d","tid":1756633,"uid":30990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T06:25:44.000Z","msg":"推   <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />全靠巴打部機先無事"},"citedBy":